<a href="/articles/26963.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26963/indexMediumPc2/26963.gif?1463480350" alt="可口可乐奥运营销，每一个元素都用得中规中矩">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/18/medium/18.png?1411569398" alt="商业">
			<span>商业</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">可口可乐奥运营销，每一个元素都用得中规中矩</h1>
